data.description: Beautiful single level home in one of Eagle Point's most desirable neighborhoods! The Eagle Point Golf Resort is conveniently located just around the corner. This home features four bedrooms and two bathrooms, with a split floor plan. The spacious kitchen has an island, granite counters, newer appliances, an ample pantry, plenty of storage and solid wood cabinetry. Hardwood flooring in main living areas with carpeted bedrooms and tiled bathrooms. You'll love the stacked stone gas fireplace and vaulted ceiling in the great room. Spacious primary suite has a slider to the cedar sauna on the rear covered patio. Enjoy the soaking tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet in the primary bath. This home is a MUST TOUR!!
